# RAG-pipeline-for-medical-Q-A
Excited to share a project I built as part of the Gen AI and AI Application module at Warwick Business School 🎓 I designed and implemented a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) pipeline for medical Q&amp;A, using a weighted Reciprocal Rank Fusion (RRF) approach to improve how relevant evidence is retrieved and ranked before being passed to the model.
